title: BetterZip 2.3.1 Patched
description:
BetterZip 2.3.1 compression, uncompression and Viewer Archive utility


Create scalable archives in most common formats and clean them of unecessary files.
  
Update Edit archived files in an external application and BetterZip can update your archive.
  
Preview files in your archives without extracting or use Quick Look.
  
Protect your data with unbreakable AES-256 encryption.
   
The BetterZip 2 Services & Archive Operations Queue
BetterZip 2 lets you create and extract archives through services that can be started through the Finder contextual menu or even keyboard shortcuts. And the new queue helps you create and extract a large number of archives in an ordered way.

System requirement : from MacOS X 10.5.x to MacOS X 10.8.x

Archive Compression, viewing, editing and split: Zip, 7-zip, Tar, Gzip, Bzip2, Xar, Rar(optional).

Archive Expanssion (most of archives format) :
ARJ, LZH, ISO, CHM, CAB, CPIO, DEB, RPM, StuffIt SIT, BinHex, MacBinary, .zip, .jar, .war, .ear, .sar, .par, .wsr, .rar, .cbz, .cbr, .tar, .tgz, .tbz, .gz, .bz, .bz2, .cpio, .cpgz, .7z, .lha, .lzh, .arj, .iso, .chm, .cab, .deb, .rpm, .sit, .sitx, .hqx, .bin.

--------------

BetterZip is patched, no need of serial number. works fine in MacOs X 10.8.x.

Quick Look plugin is joined, works well with Mac0s 10.6.x, but is a little buggy with MacOs X 10.8.x.
